overview: Look What I Can Do 2 is an excellent film by Platinum X Pictures. The film focuses on breath taking solo performances by some Platinum X's hottest models and performers. And these hand-picked ladies have come prepared in some of their sexiest outfits and favorite toys to play with too! Featuring Jewles West, Janessa Jordan, Brooke Shine, Lola, Sandra Syn, Alex, Hunter and Victoria Zdrok!
title: Look What I Can Do 2
